oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Drawing of rabbit and bee
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A drawing of a rabbit and a bee [done in ink] by Ben Faucett. Under the bee is the letter 'a' and a larvae seems to be below it. The image is cropped so that the legs of an unidentified insect are next to the bee.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Faucett, Ben
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
